WEBVTT

00:02:58.800 --> 00:03:02.640
I asked this question to Amrita Pritam,

00:03:02.640 --> 00:03:04.640
and she said something lovely.

00:03:04.640 --> 00:03:12.560
She said to me, “Young man, 
age is like the sugar in a tea cup,

00:03:12.560 --> 00:03:14.520
and the last sip is always the sweetest!”

00:03:15.320 --> 00:03:19.200
Because as you all know,
India lives in her villages,

00:03:19.200 --> 00:03:23.800
so I decided to go to this village 
outside Bangalore.

00:03:23.800 --> 00:03:27.880
There I met this lady named Thimaka.

00:03:27.880 --> 00:03:31.520
She did not have children. 
She told us a beautiful story.